### 1️⃣ Add a New Journal Entry
POST http://localhost:3000/api/journal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "entryDate": "2024-02-25",
  "mood": "Happy",
  "reflections": "Had a great day!",
  "gratitude": "Thankful for my family."
}

### 2️⃣ Delete a Journal Entry
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/journal/2

### 3️⃣ Get a Journal Entry by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/journal/2

### 4️⃣ Get All Journal Entries for a User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/journal/user/1

### 5️⃣ Get Journal Entries by Date Range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/journal/user/1/date-range?startDate=2024-02-01&endDate=2024-02-20

### 6️⃣ Get Journal Statistics for a User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/journal/user/1/stats

### 7️⃣ Update a Journal Entry
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/journal/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "Excited",
  "reflections": "Looking forward to my trip!",
  "gratitude": "Grateful for new opportunities."
}

### 8️⃣ Get All Journal Entries
GET http://localhost:3000/api/journal/all

